          "title": "Math Mid Prepare",
          "content": "\\*\\*Must-cover tests\n\\*\\*\n. Nth-Term Test for Divergence. ✅\n\n. Integral Test. ✅\n\n. Direct Comparison Test. ✅\n\n. Limit Comparison Test. ✅\n\n. Alternating Series Test. ✅\n\n. Absolute Convergence check ✅\n\n. Conditional Convergence check ✅\n\n. Ratio Test. ✅\n\n. Root Test. ✅\n\n**Also know these patterns**\n\n. P-series recognition: ✅\n\n. Geometric-series recognition ❌",
